{"type":"message","id":"8d37a3d3","parentId":"b800ee5f","timestamp":"2026-03-02T02:38:40.323Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Coding Agent\n\n让我先解释**会话管理问题**：\n\n**子会话隔离**是指对于长时间或复杂的任务（比如处理GitHub issues、创建PR等），应该使用 `sessions_spawn` 创建独立的子会话来执行，而不是在主会话中直接运行。这样做的好处是：\n\n1. **避免中断** - 主会话超时不会影响子会话的执行\n2. **资源隔离** - 子会话有自己的上下文和内存空间\n3. **错误隔离** - 子会话出错不会影响主会话\n4. **并行处理** - 可以同时处理多个任务\n\n现在让我更新HEARTBEAT.md文件：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_906db2adeaaf4ab99602e29d","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/coding/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md","content":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Coding Agent Health Checks\n\n## Open Source Contribution Monitoring (rotate 2-4× daily)\n- [ ] **GitHub Issue Tracking**: Check assigned repositories for new issues requiring attention\n- [ ] **PR Status Review**: Monitor submitted pull requests for review feedback and merge status\n- [ ] **Contribution Progress**: Track coding contribution metrics and community recognition\n- [ ] **Code Quality Assurance**: Ensure all submissions pass CI/CD and follow project standards\n- [ ] **Community Engagement**: Monitor GitHub discussions and community interactions\n\n## Project Management Tasks\n- [ ] **Repository Monitoring**: Verify daily issue checks on assigned projects (OpenClaw Core)\n- [ ] **Issue Prioritization**: Review good first issue / help wanted labels for next tasks\n- [ ] **Documentation Updates**: Ensure technical documentation is current and accurate\n- [ ] **Skill Development**: Identify areas for improvement in coding expertise\n\n## The ONE Framework Alignment\n- **价值 (50%)**: Building open source reputation and technical portfolio\n- **专业 (30%)**: CS certification support through practical coding experience  \n- **梦想 (20%)**: AI-MCN content generation and automation development\n\n## Alert Conditions (Reach Out When)\n- New high-priority issues in assigned repositories\n- PR review feedback requiring immediate attention\n- CI/CD failures on submitted code\n- Community recognition or mentions from maintainers\n- Blocked tasks needing human input\n\n## Silent Mode (Reply HEARTBEAT_OK)\n- No new issues or PR activity since last check\n- All contributions progressing normally\n- Checked within last 4 hours\n- Outside active development hours (23:00-08:00)\n\n## Daily Summary Process\n**Daily work summary content source**: \n- **Primary Source**: Session records in `/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/coding/sessions/` directory (.jsonl format)\n- **Content Extraction**: GitHub issue monitoring, PR creation, code reviews, community interactions, and other open source contribution activities from daily interactions\n- **Output Location**: Structured output to `agents/coding/workspace/memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- **Delivery**: Daily summary report sent to Telegram group at 23:30\n\n---\n*Coding Agent heartbeat checklist - Updated: 2026-03-02*"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":21963,"output":675,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22638,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772419098423}}
