{"type":"message","id":"87c7f2d7","parentId":"dbba500f","timestamp":"2026-03-02T04:07:06.889Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在让我检查这个目录是否是OpenClaw仓库：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0f39a6d798f74aaa8e356de8","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/README.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":32876,"output":40,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32916,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772424423154}}
{"type":"message","id":"46635129","parentId":"87c7f2d7","timestamp":"2026-03-02T04:07:06.907Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_0f39a6d798f74aaa8e356de8","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# OpenClaw Agent Runtime Directory\n\nThis directory contains the complete runtime environment for OpenClaw AI agents.\n\n## Directory Structure\n\n```\n.openclaw/\n├── agents/                 # Individual agent workspaces and state\n│   └── main/              # Core agent workspace (current)\n│       └── workspace/     # Core agent's working directory\n├── workspace/             # Global shared workspace\n├── memory/                # Memory system and SQLite search index\n├── cron/                  # Scheduled job configurations\n├── credentials/           # Channel authentication credentials\n├── logs/                  # System and agent activity logs\n├── telegram/              # Telegram channel data\n├── devices/               # Paired device information\n├── mem0/                  # Vector memory storage\n├── browser/               # Browser automation cache\n├── canvas/                # Canvas UI rendering data\n├── identity/              # Agent identity configurations\n├── completions/           # Auto-completion caches\n├── subagents/             # Sub-agent runtime data\n├── delivery-queue/        # Message delivery queue\n├── openclaw.json          # Main configuration file\n├── config.yaml            # Auxiliary configuration\n├── gateway.env            # Gateway environment variables\n├── exec-approvals.json    # Execution approval records\n└── update-check.json      # Update check metadata\n```\n\n## Key Components\n\n### Agents\n- **Core Agent**: Located at `agents/main/workspace`\n- **Role**: System coordinator, user interface, multi-agent orchestration\n- **Permissions**: Full macOS system access\n\n### Memory System\n- **Long-term**: `MEMORY.md` - Curated knowledge and system configuration\n- **Daily logs**: `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` - Raw activity logs\n- **Search index**: SQLite database for semantic memory retrieval\n\n### Configuration\n- **Primary**: `openclaw.json` - Main configuration with channel tokens and agent settings\n- **Backup**: Multiple `.bak` versions maintained automatically\n- **Environment**: `gateway.env` - Runtime environment variables\n\n### Security\n- **Credentials**: Stored in `credentials/` directory with restricted permissions\n- **Execution approvals**: Recorded in `exec-approvals.json`\n- **Isolation**: Each agent maintains separate workspace and state\n\n## Usage Guidelines\n\n- **Do not manually modify** files in this directory unless you understand the implications\n- **Backup regularly**: The system automatically backs up configuration files\n- **Agent autonomy**: Each agent manages its own workspace independently\n- **Memory persistence**: Important decisions should be recorded in MEMORY.md or daily logs\n\n## Related Projects\n\n- **AI-Note**: [https://github.com/Linux2010/ai-note](https://github.com/Linux2010/ai-note)\n  - AI-friendly technical documentation repository\n  - Contains OpenClaw architecture and solution guides\n\n---\n**Generated**: 2026-02-27  \n**Agent**: core  \n**Host**: hope's Mac mini"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772424426900}}
