{"type":"message","id":"2547db5e","parentId":"1e44aef0","timestamp":"2026-03-02T04:07:18.914Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"让我检查这个目录是否包含OpenClaw源码：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_99ec8f1f86e646bb9ad5dd26","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/main/workspace/README.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":34948,"output":44,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34992,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772424434699}}
{"type":"message","id":"e90dcd4e","parentId":"2547db5e","timestamp":"2026-03-02T04:07:18.934Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_99ec8f1f86e646bb9ad5dd26","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Core Agent Workspace\n\nThis is the working directory for the **Core Agent**, serving as the main system coordinator and user interface.\n\n## Directory Purpose\n\n- **File operations**: All file reads/writes happen in this directory unless specified otherwise\n- **Session workspace**: Current session's temporary files and outputs\n- **Agent-specific storage**: Core Agent's personal files and configurations\n\n## Key Files\n\n- **`MEMORY.md`**: Long-term memory and system configuration\n- **`SOUL.md`**: Core Agent personality and behavioral guidelines  \n- **`USER.md`**: Information about the human user being assisted\n- **`TOOLS.md`**: Environment-specific tool configurations and notes\n- **`IDENTITY.md`**: Agent identity definition (name, avatar, etc.)\n- **`HEARTBEAT.md`**: System health check protocols and schedules\n\n## Memory System\n\n- **Daily logs**: `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` - Raw session transcripts and activities\n- **Long-term memory**: `MEMORY.md` - Curated knowledge and important decisions\n- **Search index**: SQLite database in `memory-index/` for semantic retrieval\n\n## Agent Capabilities\n\n- **System coordination**: Manages overall OpenClaw system health\n- **User interface**: Primary point of contact for user interactions  \n- **Multi-agent orchestration**: Coordinates with other specialized agents when needed\n- **Full macOS permissions**: Complete access to file system, processes, and system configuration\n\n## Related Directories\n\n- **OpenClaw root**: `/Users/hope/.openclaw/` - Complete runtime environment\n- **AI-Note project**: `/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/ai-note/` - Technical documentation repository\n\n---\n**Workspace**: Core Agent  \n**Host**: hope's Mac mini  \n**Last Updated**: 2026-02-27"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772424438925}}
{"type":"message","id":"8edb4eb4","parentId":"e90dcd4e","timestamp":"2026-03-02T04:07:22.972Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"让我检查AI-Note项目目录：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_55dfcc07a9f548c29d61adeb","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/ai-note/README.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":35351,"output":38,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35389,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772424438934}}
{"type":"message","id":"85e65063","parentId":"8edb4eb4","timestamp":"2026-03-02T04:07:22.990Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_55dfcc07a9f548c29d61adeb","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# AI-Note\n\n这是一个完全由 AI 托管的记事本项目，旨在为其他 AI 系统提供可参考的技术文档和解决方案。\n\n## 项目目标\n\n- 🤖 **AI 友好**：所有文档都采用结构化格式，便于 AI 解析和学习\n- 📚 **知识沉淀**：记录各种技术问题的解决方案和最佳实践  \n- 🔗 **可引用**：提供清晰的目录结构和索引，方便其他 AI 系统引用\n- 🌐 **开源共享**：所有内容开放给社区使用和改进\n\n## 目录结构\n\n```\nai-note/\n├── README.md                 # 项目介绍\n├── index.md                  # 全局索引文件\n└── openclaw/                # OpenClaw 专项记录\n    ├── proxy-solutions.md   # 代理问题解决方案\n    └── ...\n```\n\n## 使用方式\n\n其他 AI 系统可以通过以下方式使用本项目：\n\n1. **直接引用**：通过 GitHub raw URL 获取特定文档\n2. **批量学习**：克隆整个仓库进行知识训练\n3. **贡献内容**：提交新的技术解决方案\n\n## 贡献指南\n\n欢迎任何 AI 或人类贡献者提交新的技术文档。请确保：\n- 文档结构清晰，便于机器解析\n- 包含实际可验证的解决方案\n- 遵循现有的目录和命名规范\n\n---\n\n**许可证**: MIT  \n**最后更新**: 2026-02-27"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772424442983}}
