{"type":"message","id":"447cf35f","parentId":"7fc56684","timestamp":"2026-03-02T10:11:55.599Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Coding Agent - 就绪状态报告\n\n### **当前仓库配置问题**\n我发现了一个关键问题：您的本地OpenClaw仓库 (`/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/openclaw`) 当前只配置了**官方仓库**作为远程：\n\n```\norigin: https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw.git\n```\n\n**缺少您的个人fork远程配置**，这会导致：\n- ❌ 无法推送代码到您的fork\n- ❌ 无法创建Pull Request\n- ❌ 贡献工作流程中断\n\n### **GitHub Fork地址确认**\n根据搜索结果，您的GitHub用户名是 **Linux2010**，但我在公开搜索中**没有找到您fork的openclaw仓库**。\n\n### **标准贡献工作流程（来自skills）**\n正确的流程应该是：\n1. **Fork官方仓库** → `https://github.com/Linux2010/openclaw`\n2. **克隆您的fork** → `git clone https://github.com/Linux2010/openclaw.git`\n3. **添加upstream远程** → `git remote add upstream https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw.git`\n4. **基于main创建特性分支** → `git checkout -b fix/issue-number-description`\n\n### **当前就绪状态**\n- ⚠️ **仓库配置不完整** - 缺少个人fork远程\n- ⚠️ **无法执行贡献** - 没有推送权限到官方仓库\n- ✅ **本地仓库存在** - `/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/openclaw`\n- ✅ **工作流程已定义** - 标准贡献流程已记录在MEMORY.md\n\n### **建议行动**\n1. **确认您的fork是否存在** - 请访问 `https://github.com/Linux2010/openclaw`\n2. **如果不存在** - 先在GitHub网页上fork官方仓库\n3. **更新本地配置** - 添加您的fork作为origin，官方仓库作为upstream\n\n您希望我帮您完成这些配置步骤吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":82698,"output":434,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83132,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772446278933}}
