{"type":"message","id":"066c8a02","parentId":"f99cbe47","timestamp":"2026-03-02T10:57:13.425Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Coding Agent - 就绪状态确认\n\n### **当前仓库配置状态**\n✅ **正确配置** - 您的本地仓库已经正确设置：\n- **Origin**: `https://github.com/Linux2010/openclaw.git` (您的个人fork)\n- **需要添加**: upstream远程指向官方仓库\n\n### **Fork Main分支同步保障**\n\n根据您在MEMORY.md中定义的最佳实践，我将确保：\n\n#### **1. 初始化upstream配置**\n```bash\ngit remote add upstream https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw.git\ngit fetch upstream\n```\n\n#### **2. 保持main分支同步流程**\n每次工作前执行：\n```bash\ngit checkout main\ngit fetch upstream  \ngit reset --hard upstream/main\ngit push origin main --force\n```\n\n#### **3. 特性分支开发**\n```bash\ngit checkout main\ngit checkout -b fix/issue-number-description\n# 开发工作...\ngit push origin fix/issue-number-description\n```\n\n### **自动化保障机制**\n- **子会话隔离**: 所有贡献任务通过 `sessions_spawn` 在独立会话中执行\n- **心跳监控**: 每4小时检查仓库状态和新issues\n- **安全重置**: 使用 `git reset --hard` 确保main分支始终与官方完全一致\n- **分支保护**: 绝不在main分支上直接提交，所有开发在特性分支进行\n\n### **当前就绪状态**\n✅ **仓库地址正确**: `/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/openclaw`  \n✅ **Fork配置正确**: origin指向您的个人fork  \n⚠️ **待完成**: 添加upstream远程配置  \n✅ **工作流程完整**: 标准贡献流程已定义并可执行\n\n您希望我立即添加upstream配置并开始监控新的GitHub issues吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":83587,"output":389,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83976,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772448998237}}
